[The case fatality rate is staying around 50 per cent, which reflects how
the addicts infect themselves by injection and the probability that the
contamination is "chunky": in anthrax lethality is a direct function of
dose. Past experience suggests that new cases will appear over the next
couple of months. - Mod.MHJ]
